<p>写生作品 25×50cm</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200922/b0dad6a7640d4930a582e8752dcc434a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>岠嵎山写生45×65cm</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200922/2a8d86651fee41428f258dc4a77ce680.png" max-width="600" /></p>
